{
  "stem": "10710.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I was-- I got along very well with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So I had a very easy job there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I can't complain on Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And Schindler used to come there quite often because Banker was there often.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we used to have a stove because that's how we kept warm there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And the stove had two bottoms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was in the middle a bottom and then the top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So we used to cook on the middle bottom there all kind of food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And Schindler used to come and he used to ask me, what's cooking today, if he smelled it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But the Germans didn't-- the wacht-- they couldn't do anything to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And when Passover came, Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Banker told me he's not going to eat any bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I mean, there wasn't too much bread but he had enough bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "So I cooked for him all kinds of stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I cook for him [NON-ENGLISH] and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And he was-- he and there was a rabbi, Levertov, who is in the book, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "In Schindler's list, original list when he-- and I was helping him to eat Passover.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And I already stole a little bit for myself, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "So I don't have to buy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We even have-- they baked two, three matzohs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we had the electric ovens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "So people baked some matzoh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Everybody got a little piece, you know, to make a bracha when Pesach came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And in the camp, in Brunnlitz, there was the commander.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "His name was-- I have it written down on a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Sometimes I forget already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And he was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "He was sent from [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] from a big camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Leopold was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And he couldn't do anything because Schindler was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "Once Schindler wasn't there, he showed his what he could do.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
